  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "The config [docs](https://lyft.github.io/envoy/docs/configuration/overview/overview.html) mention watchdog configuration options, but they are not listed in the json [schema](https://github.com/lyft/envoy/blob/master/source/common/json/config_schemas.cc#L1092), so adding these configurations causes config schema validation failure.\r\n\r\nThe relevant options are:\r\n```\r\nwatchdog_miss_timeout_ms\r\nwatchdog_megamiss_timeout_ms\r\nwatchdog_kill_timeout_ms\r\nwatchdog_multikill_timeout_ms\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt's friday night for me, so i'm opening a ticket instead of a PR, but if nobody gets around to this, i'll go ahead and fix it.",
